General.Name: Jerash Holdings US Inc
General.Description: Jerash Holdings (US), Inc., through its subsidiaries, manufactures and exports customized and ready-made sport and outerwear. The company offers t-shirts, jackets, vests, pants and shorts, and polo shirts made from knitted fabric, as well as personal protective equipment. It serves various brand-name retailers in the United States, Hong Kong, Germany, Jordan, and internationally. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Fairfield, New Jersey.
